WEBVTT

01:44.400 --> 01:47.280
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:50.000 --> 01:52.680
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

01:54.720 --> 01:56.320
Madam Chen.

01:57.800 --> 01:58.800
You're late.

01:58.880 --> 02:00.640
You'll have to drink
a penalty toast later.

02:02.480 --> 02:04.240
Madam Chen.

02:04.320 --> 02:05.160
Madam Liu.

02:06.040 --> 02:09.120
Ladies, look at Madam Song's attire today.

02:09.199 --> 02:11.360
She's looking more and more noble.

02:12.200 --> 02:14.040
You flatter me, Madam Liu.

02:14.120 --> 02:16.520
It's truly an honor to be invited

02:16.600 --> 02:18.640
by all of you today.

02:19.160 --> 02:20.720
‎WIFE OF MERCHANT CHEN,
‎WIFE OF REGISTRAR HU

02:20.800 --> 02:21.960
‎WIFE OF COUNTY MILITARY OFFICER LIU

02:22.040 --> 02:24.760
An imperial green jade bracelet.

02:25.960 --> 02:27.840
It's truly rare.

02:28.640 --> 02:29.880
Just look at the translucency

02:29.960 --> 02:31.320
and the color.

02:31.400 --> 02:32.800
It must be worth a fortune.

02:33.880 --> 02:34.800
Let's walk and talk.

02:34.880 --> 02:36.000
Let's walk and talk.

02:36.080 --> 02:37.440
Come on, ladies.

02:37.520 --> 02:38.440
This bracelet

02:38.520 --> 02:40.720
was simply a meeting gift
from the magistrate's wife.

02:40.800 --> 02:43.720
-No wonder. It's from the bride's mother!
-Yes.

02:44.280 --> 02:45.640
-Ah!
-Excuse me.

02:45.720 --> 02:47.200
You clumsy girl.

02:47.280 --> 02:48.680
You… What are you doing here?

02:50.760 --> 02:52.920
You didn't follow me here
to cause trouble, did you?

02:53.520 --> 02:56.200
What, you bought this place?

02:56.720 --> 02:58.160
You're allowed here, but I'm not?

02:58.720 --> 02:59.560
You know each other?

02:59.640 --> 03:01.520
No, I don't know her.

03:02.960 --> 03:04.600
Madam Liu, let me tell you.

03:05.120 --> 03:08.520
My son's marriage
was personally arranged by the magistrate.

03:08.600 --> 03:11.200
The magistrate comes from
a distinguished scholarly family.

03:11.280 --> 03:13.560
-Do come more often.
-They value character and refinement.

03:13.640 --> 03:15.760
The betrothal gifts
followed ancient custom.

03:16.440 --> 03:18.200
The bride's dowry was generous.

03:19.560 --> 03:20.760
In marriage,

03:20.840 --> 03:23.160
-what matters is a proper match in status.
-Enjoy. Just call if you need anything.

03:23.240 --> 03:25.360
If someone lacks character and refinement,

03:25.440 --> 03:28.240
such a marriage must never happen.

03:28.320 --> 03:30.160
-Exactly.
-Am I right?

03:30.240 --> 03:31.800
The magistrate is truly generous.

03:31.880 --> 03:33.360
Congratulations.

03:33.440 --> 03:35.560
Sold your son for a fine price, did you?

03:35.640 --> 03:37.040
-You…
-This…

03:37.880 --> 03:38.800
Cursed girl.

03:42.560 --> 03:43.560
Let's hurry inside.

03:44.160 --> 03:47.000
Don't let someone so vulgar ruin our mood.

03:47.080 --> 03:48.400
Right? Come along.

03:48.480 --> 03:49.720
Who is she talking about?

03:49.800 --> 03:51.880
-She's talking nonsense.
-What?

03:53.360 --> 03:55.360
I offer you both a toast.

03:58.960 --> 04:01.080
You are most seasoned

04:01.160 --> 04:02.320
in the ways of hospitality.

04:03.080 --> 04:05.000
You clearly know many people, Ms. Yu.

04:08.280 --> 04:11.240
We welcome guests from every quarter.
Harmony yields prosperity.

04:11.840 --> 04:12.880
In business,

04:12.960 --> 04:15.160
it never hurts to know more friends.

04:17.800 --> 04:19.399
Please enjoy yourselves.

04:20.120 --> 04:21.680
I must attend to other guests.

04:34.560 --> 04:36.640
Ms. Yu, what's wrong?

04:36.720 --> 04:37.640
You don't look well.

04:40.000 --> 04:41.960
Just now, inside,
that man brushed my hand.

04:42.720 --> 04:45.200
I don't know why, but that brief touch

04:45.800 --> 04:47.480
frightened me.

04:48.080 --> 04:49.520
Another guest trying to take advantage?

04:50.760 --> 04:52.080
How shameless.

04:52.880 --> 04:54.840
It's not exactly about that.

04:56.240 --> 04:57.920
I just feel like I've seen him before.

05:00.080 --> 05:02.640
Who was that young lady
you were talking to?

05:03.760 --> 05:06.680
Oh, her? Her name is Fan Changyu.

05:07.400 --> 05:10.280
She was the notorious curse of Xigu Alley.

05:11.280 --> 05:12.960
The fortune-tellers all say

05:13.040 --> 05:15.920
she was born under
a once-in-a-thousand-years calamity star.

05:16.720 --> 05:18.560
She not only brought misfortune
upon her parents,

05:18.640 --> 05:21.040
she even caused her uncle's death.

05:21.120 --> 05:22.560
The matter even ended up in court.

05:22.640 --> 05:23.640
And

05:23.720 --> 05:25.040
just this month,

05:25.120 --> 05:27.720
a group of bandits
broke into her home in the dead of night.

05:28.320 --> 05:30.280
Several people were killed.

05:30.360 --> 05:33.440
The whole of Lin'an knows about it.

05:36.640 --> 05:37.680
Who knows

05:37.760 --> 05:40.040
how many men have touched
those hands of hers.

05:40.120 --> 05:42.800
No wonder she became so composed

05:42.880 --> 05:44.320
and utterly without decorum.

05:45.200 --> 05:47.280
I searched for years and never found her.

05:47.800 --> 05:51.200
I never expected her
to be thriving here in Lin'an

05:51.920 --> 05:53.840
and associating with so many men.

05:58.240 --> 06:00.440
Perhaps it's only business dealings.

06:01.960 --> 06:03.200
Still making excuses for her?

06:03.800 --> 06:04.960
I wouldn't dare.

06:06.040 --> 06:08.480
She left false clues
about fleeing beyond the frontier.

06:08.560 --> 06:10.360
I searched for six years in vain.

06:11.800 --> 06:14.840
I never imagined that in just six years
she would establish herself

06:15.360 --> 06:16.960
and open such a grand restaurant.

06:19.120 --> 06:20.560
She is not to be underestimated.

06:21.280 --> 06:22.120
Understood.

06:22.720 --> 06:24.960
I will investigate
her connections at once.

06:25.840 --> 06:27.680
And investigate the men
around her as well.

06:27.760 --> 06:29.160
Whoever has touched her,

06:29.720 --> 06:31.840
cut off the hand that did it.

06:31.920 --> 06:33.720
Bring it to me.

06:35.640 --> 06:36.520
Yes.

06:37.240 --> 06:38.840
I will carry out your orders at once.

06:43.000 --> 06:45.760
Why would Ms. Yu hire someone like her?

06:45.840 --> 06:48.120
Nothing is worse for a restaurant
than bad luck.

06:49.280 --> 06:53.440
Perhaps Ms. Yu
doesn't know her background.

06:53.520 --> 06:55.160
That's how a jinx got in.

06:56.280 --> 06:58.200
-Ladies.
-Ms. Yu.

06:58.280 --> 06:59.920
What jinx?

07:01.960 --> 07:04.120
Yixiang Restaurant
does not serve such a dish.

07:04.920 --> 07:05.760
Ms. Yu,

07:06.440 --> 07:09.040
we truly mean well.

07:09.120 --> 07:11.760
That jinx brings death wherever she goes!

07:12.560 --> 07:13.440
Really?

07:14.440 --> 07:16.800
From what I heard,

07:16.880 --> 07:19.400
she supported her scholar fiancé
for years,

07:20.000 --> 07:22.960
and after he passed the provincial exam,
he broke off the engagement.

07:23.680 --> 07:25.120
If you ask me,

07:25.200 --> 07:27.040
that ungrateful fiancé and his mother

07:27.120 --> 07:28.360
were the real curse.

07:28.960 --> 07:31.760
Not only did it harm that young lady,
it ruined her parents as well.

07:36.040 --> 07:37.680
Then perhaps all that talk

07:37.760 --> 07:40.040
of her being a jinx is just rumor.

07:40.800 --> 07:42.760
Madam Liu is right.

07:42.840 --> 07:46.160
Mrs. Fan has been
raising her little sister on her own.

07:46.240 --> 07:48.120
Ever since she came to Yixiang Restaurant,

07:48.200 --> 07:50.720
my braised pork
has been selling better than ever.

07:50.800 --> 07:53.400
If you ask me, she's a lucky charm.

07:56.600 --> 07:57.720
But Madam Song,

07:58.320 --> 08:00.920
who told you she was a jinx?

08:05.320 --> 08:08.320
Just hearsay.

08:10.200 --> 08:13.200
Why must women make things difficult
for one another?

08:13.280 --> 08:14.920
Spreading gossip all day

08:15.000 --> 08:17.000
will invite retribution.

08:18.200 --> 08:19.600
You're educated and sensible.

08:19.680 --> 08:22.680
How could you stoop to such filthy gossip?

08:22.760 --> 08:24.560
You must have been misled.

08:30.600 --> 08:32.280
Why hasn't all the food been served?

08:32.880 --> 08:33.840
I'll go hurry them.

08:33.919 --> 08:35.520
Ladies, please enjoy.

08:35.600 --> 08:36.559
Of course.

08:49.880 --> 08:50.720
You didn't know?

08:50.800 --> 08:52.520
That proprietress Yu Qianqian

08:53.320 --> 08:55.360
was with child before she was ever wed.

08:55.440 --> 08:57.160
The child she once carried…

08:57.240 --> 08:59.640
No one even knew who the father was.

09:00.760 --> 09:03.720
"Why must women make things difficult
for one another?" How noble.

09:04.480 --> 09:07.520
If you ask me,
she's no different from Fan Changyu.

09:07.600 --> 09:09.760
A shameless woman with no virtue.

09:11.600 --> 09:13.920
Let's not allow idle gossip

09:14.000 --> 09:15.960
to spoil our gathering.

09:16.040 --> 09:17.080
Quite right.

09:17.160 --> 09:18.000
Let's get back to it.

09:29.080 --> 09:31.200
A flock of chattering gossips.

09:31.880 --> 09:33.080
According to them,

09:33.680 --> 09:36.040
the child may be hiding
inside the restaurant.

09:39.360 --> 09:40.480
The one who talked the most…

09:41.600 --> 09:42.760
Teach her a lesson.

09:46.640 --> 09:47.640
Yes.

09:48.240 --> 09:50.120
-Madam Liu.
-You think I'm drunk?

09:50.200 --> 09:51.240
You are drunk.

09:51.320 --> 09:54.400
Then I must trouble you
to put in a few good words for me

09:54.480 --> 09:55.400
before the magistrate.

09:55.480 --> 09:58.160
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

10:12.560 --> 10:14.680
Lecturing me about retribution?

10:17.080 --> 10:19.120
If there truly is divine retribution,

10:19.640 --> 10:21.560
it should fall on that wretched girl.

10:22.160 --> 10:25.080
If Heaven truly has eyes,

10:25.720 --> 10:27.760
it should strike that wretched girl--

10:42.480 --> 10:45.440
Mind your words before you speak.

10:46.200 --> 10:47.880
Watch that filthy mouth of yours.

10:48.480 --> 10:49.880
If you speak such nonsense again,

10:50.400 --> 10:51.840
you won't get off so lightly.

10:53.200 --> 10:55.000
Yes, yes… I understand.

11:00.000 --> 11:01.200
Madam!

11:01.280 --> 11:02.320
Madam!

11:02.840 --> 11:03.840
Madam!

11:05.040 --> 11:08.480
‎FANG'S TEA SHOP

11:14.320 --> 11:15.520
PORK TONGUE

11:16.280 --> 11:17.400
PORK BELLY

11:17.480 --> 11:19.040
FAN'S BRAISED MEAT

11:19.120 --> 11:20.400
Any more pig ears?

11:20.480 --> 11:21.480
All sold out.

11:21.560 --> 11:23.280
-Come back tomorrow.
-All right.

11:24.440 --> 11:26.000
The New Year is nearly upon us.

11:26.080 --> 11:28.400
Our braised pork is selling
better than ever.

11:28.480 --> 11:29.560
You've had it hard.

11:29.640 --> 11:31.720
Not as hard as you.
You do so much each day.

11:32.720 --> 11:34.440
Earning a living is never easy.

11:35.080 --> 11:38.160
Still, though our braised pork sells well,

11:38.240 --> 11:40.120
if we want to grow further,

11:40.200 --> 11:42.680
we could design an emblem
for our braised pork.

11:42.760 --> 11:44.080
An emblem?

11:45.080 --> 11:48.400
But my braised pork is either
sliced and plated for serving

11:48.960 --> 11:51.520
or wrapped in oiled paper for takeaway.

11:51.600 --> 11:52.800
What use would an emblem be?

11:52.880 --> 11:54.440
Extremely useful.

11:55.520 --> 11:56.360
Walk with me.

11:59.520 --> 12:00.480
Look up.

12:00.560 --> 12:02.240
The shops downstairs,

12:02.840 --> 12:05.160
the Fang family's tea,
the Li family's wine,

12:05.240 --> 12:06.680
don't they each have their emblem?

12:06.760 --> 12:08.560
And each emblem is distinct.

12:08.640 --> 12:09.280
HUA

12:09.360 --> 12:11.360
You can tell at a glance whose shop it is.

12:11.440 --> 12:13.360
Once you decide on the emblem,

12:13.440 --> 12:15.760
hang a cloth banner next to the signboard.

12:15.840 --> 12:17.080
So it can be seen from afar.

12:17.160 --> 12:18.560
Then prepare more oiled paper

12:18.640 --> 12:20.040
and print the emblem on it.

12:20.120 --> 12:22.240
Wrap the meat in the printed paper.

12:22.320 --> 12:24.280
Our name will soon surpass
the Wang family's.

12:25.120 --> 12:25.960
Very well.

12:26.040 --> 12:28.200
I'll find you

12:28.280 --> 12:29.840
a scholar with decent calligraphy.

12:29.920 --> 12:31.680
Let's get this done today.

12:32.520 --> 12:33.360
Qian.

12:33.880 --> 12:36.400
My husband writes as well.

12:36.480 --> 12:37.360
I'll ask him.

12:38.280 --> 12:40.920
Is his calligraphy any good?

12:41.000 --> 12:42.600
Excellent.

12:42.680 --> 12:43.720
Truly.

12:45.040 --> 12:46.440
Even better than his face.

12:48.120 --> 12:49.400
That good?

12:49.920 --> 12:52.600
What, is he the reincarnation
of Wang Xizhi or Zhong You?

12:52.680 --> 12:53.680
Wang Xi…

12:57.080 --> 13:00.600
Though I don't know who they are,

13:00.680 --> 13:02.000
I'd say he's just as good.

13:03.320 --> 13:04.640
Changyu,

13:04.720 --> 13:07.400
I truly admire your spirit.

13:07.920 --> 13:10.320
FAN

13:14.720 --> 13:17.240
Your handwriting is so refined.

13:17.320 --> 13:18.920
I agree. In all my years

13:19.000 --> 13:22.480
running this shop,
I've never seen handwriting so fine.

13:22.560 --> 13:23.800
Remarkable indeed.

13:23.880 --> 13:25.320
So beautifully written. Ms. Yu, look.

13:28.440 --> 13:29.520
FAN

13:29.600 --> 13:31.080
It's beautiful.

13:33.000 --> 13:34.160
Do you need a break?

13:35.040 --> 13:36.320
No need. I'll continue.

13:37.160 --> 13:38.160
Changyu.

13:38.840 --> 13:40.600
Your husband writes…

13:41.120 --> 13:42.520
Remarkably well.

13:43.520 --> 13:44.840
Better than Wang…

13:46.080 --> 13:47.680
Whatever his name was. Far better.

13:47.760 --> 13:51.520
All right. Beauty lies
in the eye of the beholder.

13:51.600 --> 13:54.240
Exactly. Anything Zheng writes or paints

13:54.320 --> 13:56.160
is splendid to me.

13:57.080 --> 13:59.000
Fuling, take Ning upstairs for a bite.

13:59.080 --> 14:00.480
Whatever you like.

14:00.560 --> 14:02.280
Thank you, Pretty Lady.

14:02.920 --> 14:04.880
Such a sweet girl. Go ahead.

14:08.600 --> 14:09.600
Changyu.

14:09.680 --> 14:12.680
You've truly found a fine husband,
skilled in both letters and arms.

14:13.320 --> 14:14.200
You flatter me.

14:14.720 --> 14:15.720
Think nothing of it.

14:16.440 --> 14:17.800
From now on,

14:17.880 --> 14:19.560
we must stand together

14:19.640 --> 14:21.600
and show those gossipers

14:21.680 --> 14:23.720
that we women can achieve
great things too.

14:27.200 --> 14:30.400
FAN

14:31.000 --> 14:32.880
-I want some.
-Me too.

14:32.960 --> 14:35.920
-Me too.
-Me too.

14:46.440 --> 14:48.440
Qian, you're incredible.

14:48.520 --> 14:50.160
You said the emblem would draw a crowd,

14:50.240 --> 14:51.560
and look at them all.

14:52.280 --> 14:54.000
You're mistaken.

14:54.080 --> 14:57.080
The one drawing them in is your husband.

14:58.120 --> 14:59.960
FAN'S BRAISED MEAT

15:09.440 --> 15:10.920
Why are you still staring?

15:11.000 --> 15:12.000
Go help.

15:12.600 --> 15:13.600
Go on.

15:20.240 --> 15:21.440
Let me help.

15:25.160 --> 15:26.080
Here.

15:31.360 --> 15:32.480
Isn't this what you ordered?

15:40.960 --> 15:41.960
It was just wrapped.

15:42.640 --> 15:43.760
It was.

15:46.320 --> 15:47.240
Is his different?

15:47.320 --> 15:49.600
Yes, the one he handed out
smells even better.

15:51.600 --> 15:52.920
-I want some too!
-Me too.

15:53.000 --> 15:53.920
-Give it here!
-Give it here

15:57.160 --> 15:59.040
-Mine! Give it here.
-I want some too!

15:59.120 --> 16:00.680
Here. This is yours.

16:05.240 --> 16:08.680
Come on, come on!

16:08.760 --> 16:11.400
Come on, come on!

16:13.120 --> 16:15.120
It's all right, it's all right.

16:18.400 --> 16:19.680
You've done it wrong.

16:21.880 --> 16:23.080
No rush, sir.

16:23.160 --> 16:24.160
No need to hurry.

16:28.400 --> 16:30.560
‎-He's quite dashing.
‎-So handsome.

16:34.080 --> 16:36.080
Too small. I cut you another piece.

16:37.480 --> 16:38.520
Here.

16:47.320 --> 16:48.680
What's it to you?

16:48.760 --> 16:50.000
Stay out of it.

16:53.560 --> 16:56.840
-I want some too.
-Me too.

16:56.920 --> 16:58.320
-Me too.
-Is there any left?

17:00.200 --> 17:01.840
I shouldn't have brought you.

17:07.000 --> 17:10.240
-Give it to me.
-I want some too. I'll pay double.

17:10.319 --> 17:12.160
-Me too.
-Me too.

17:16.400 --> 17:17.720
FAN'S BRAISED MEAT

17:25.240 --> 17:26.400
Any more left?

17:26.480 --> 17:28.200
Sorry, we're sold out for today.

17:29.480 --> 17:30.320
The ones in the back?

17:31.440 --> 17:33.360
-They're just scraps.
-Scraps are fine.

17:33.440 --> 17:34.520
Will you sell them to me?

17:35.480 --> 17:36.920
As long as you're paying.

17:37.000 --> 17:38.120
All right. Take it.

17:40.320 --> 17:42.080
Your hands are greasy.

17:42.160 --> 17:43.320
Don't smudge the paper.

17:54.600 --> 17:56.040
The writing is excellent.

17:56.120 --> 17:57.600
Wrapping meat with this

17:57.680 --> 17:59.200
is sheer waste.

18:01.360 --> 18:02.160
Truly excellent.

18:05.200 --> 18:07.360
Sheer waste?

18:09.120 --> 18:10.680
What does that mean?

18:15.240 --> 18:16.360
Let's close up.

18:19.520 --> 18:22.040
GUESTS FROM ACROSS THE REALM

18:22.720 --> 18:24.040
I'm not drunk.

18:28.520 --> 18:29.680
Take care, Mr. Wu.

18:31.520 --> 18:32.680
Qianqian.

18:34.120 --> 18:34.960
Wait in the carriage.

18:35.560 --> 18:37.240
Mr. Wu, have you enjoyed yourself?

18:37.880 --> 18:40.040
It's late. Time to go home.

18:41.000 --> 18:42.840
Why should I go home?

18:44.040 --> 18:45.560
Who doesn't know

18:46.160 --> 18:48.360
I'm a regular here?

18:48.440 --> 18:49.440
-Mr. Wu.
-Come.

18:49.520 --> 18:50.680
Have a few cups with me.

18:50.760 --> 18:52.960
I'm only saying this for your own good.

18:53.040 --> 18:54.840
If you return too late,

18:54.920 --> 18:57.120
Mrs. Wu will make a scene again.

19:02.040 --> 19:05.040
Don't use that tigress to threaten me.

19:05.120 --> 19:08.440
I'll say this.
If you don't please me today,

19:08.520 --> 19:11.760
don't even think about
running this little restaurant in peace.

19:11.840 --> 19:14.400
Mr. Wu, have some dignity.

19:14.480 --> 19:15.240
Get lost.

19:17.800 --> 19:20.160
A mere maid dares speak to me like this?

19:20.720 --> 19:23.160
-Who taught you such insolence?
-Mr. Wu, calm down.

19:23.240 --> 19:24.560
I'll drink with you.

19:26.480 --> 19:27.880
Bring the wine.

19:34.760 --> 19:35.880
Drink.

19:42.520 --> 19:43.560
A scoundrel like you

19:43.640 --> 19:45.160
dares cause trouble here?

19:45.760 --> 19:47.320
I've handled your kind before.

19:47.400 --> 19:49.880
-Send him back to Mrs. Wu.
-Yes.

19:50.760 --> 19:51.800
Let go!

19:52.320 --> 19:53.760
Who do you think you are?

19:54.360 --> 19:55.920
Let go. Let go!

19:56.640 --> 19:58.000
Do you know who I am?

20:06.440 --> 20:07.280
You wretch!

20:51.880 --> 20:52.800
Are you hurt?

21:05.960 --> 21:07.320
Take this, Mr. Qi.

21:11.840 --> 21:13.320
Master, how should we deal with him?

21:15.240 --> 21:17.160
As Ms. Yu instructed,

21:17.240 --> 21:19.320
hand him over to Mrs. Wu.

21:19.840 --> 21:22.240
Remember, keep him alive.

21:23.480 --> 21:25.360
Do not cause trouble for Ms. Yu.

21:25.440 --> 21:26.280
-Yes.
-Yes.

21:38.120 --> 21:40.560
Ms. Yu, you don't look well.

21:43.000 --> 21:44.200
Were you frightened?

21:49.840 --> 21:50.800
I'm fine.

21:52.240 --> 21:54.400
Thank you, Mr. Qi, for stepping in.

22:06.680 --> 22:07.680
I'll take my leave.

22:59.600 --> 23:01.880
Ms. Yu, are you all right?

23:08.280 --> 23:09.960
His manner is somewhat similar.

23:10.480 --> 23:12.400
But he had no scar on his face.

23:13.840 --> 23:15.640
And his voice wasn't like this.

23:17.800 --> 23:19.480
Perhaps I'm being paranoid.

23:19.560 --> 23:21.080
How could he possibly be in Lin'an?

23:21.600 --> 23:22.560
Who is it?

23:25.840 --> 23:26.880
No one.

23:33.120 --> 23:33.960
FRAGRANCE TRAVELS FAR

23:34.040 --> 23:35.840
These pastries were prepared just for you.

23:35.920 --> 23:38.200
My sister eats a great deal as well.

23:38.280 --> 23:40.280
She can eat three meals' worth
in a single sitting.

23:40.360 --> 23:42.600
Her rice bowl is as large
as a soup tureen.

23:42.680 --> 23:44.400
She's truly impressive.

23:44.480 --> 23:46.360
Have you ever seen a pig slaughtered?

23:46.960 --> 23:47.880
No.

23:48.400 --> 23:52.080
My sister can knock a pig unconscious
with a single slap.

23:53.120 --> 23:53.960
Really?

23:54.040 --> 23:56.280
I've never seen anyone
as formidable as your sister.

23:57.000 --> 23:59.120
-Fuling, come give us a hand.
-Coming.

24:00.000 --> 24:01.520
I'm stepping out for a moment.

24:02.040 --> 24:03.080
I'll be back shortly.

24:47.240 --> 24:48.560
Thief.

24:48.640 --> 24:49.920
I… I'm no thief.

24:50.000 --> 24:51.360
I don't care who you are.

24:51.440 --> 24:52.520
You're sneaking food.

24:52.600 --> 24:54.640
I'll tell my sister and Pretty Lady.

24:54.720 --> 24:57.800
-Don't.
-Changyu, someone's stealing--

24:59.160 --> 25:00.200
Please don't.

25:00.280 --> 25:01.680
Who said you could steal food?

25:01.760 --> 25:03.160
This is my house.

25:03.240 --> 25:05.120
My mother owns this place.

25:05.200 --> 25:06.240
Why shouldn't I eat?

25:06.320 --> 25:09.560
You're Pretty Lady's son?

25:09.640 --> 25:13.240
What's your name? How old are you?

25:13.320 --> 25:16.600
My name is Yu Bao'er.
I'm 6 years old. How about you?

25:16.680 --> 25:18.040
Have some more.

25:18.120 --> 25:19.800
I'll just have this one.

25:19.880 --> 25:21.360
Mother won't let me eat too much.

25:21.440 --> 25:23.680
Too many sweets will rot my teeth.

25:24.680 --> 25:25.800
What's that?

25:26.400 --> 25:27.320
It's…

25:30.560 --> 25:33.120
It's when little worms
eat away at your teeth.

25:33.200 --> 25:34.520
It hurts terribly.

25:34.600 --> 25:36.560
Worms in your teeth?

25:36.640 --> 25:39.800
Like cabbage worms? Or rice weevils?

25:39.880 --> 25:41.640
I don't know.

25:41.720 --> 25:42.800
I've never had one.

25:43.400 --> 25:45.480
Then I'd better not eat too much.

25:46.440 --> 25:48.080
Shall we go outside and play?

25:50.200 --> 25:52.240
Mother says my fate is unusual.

25:52.320 --> 25:53.920
I shouldn't see too many people.

25:54.000 --> 25:54.920
That way,

25:55.440 --> 25:56.640
I'll stay safe.

25:59.440 --> 26:02.520
Then, let's play hide-and-seek.

26:19.160 --> 26:20.240
Don't touch that.

26:21.240 --> 26:22.280
-This child…
-Go away!

26:22.360 --> 26:23.360
-Forgive us.
-Sorry!

26:32.840 --> 26:33.760
Bao'er?

26:34.600 --> 26:36.320
-Why are you here?
-This way.

26:36.400 --> 26:38.320
-Come on.
-Your mother told you not to run about.

26:40.280 --> 26:42.400
You two, stay put.

26:52.080 --> 26:53.560
What does it matter?

26:53.640 --> 26:55.480
-Just for a moment.
-Then I'll return shortly.

26:57.840 --> 26:59.040
Where did these kids come from?

26:59.760 --> 27:01.240
You're ruining my fun. Get out.

27:01.880 --> 27:02.840
Stop running.

27:03.360 --> 27:05.080
-Stop running.
-Hurry up.

27:06.160 --> 27:08.040
You little brats dare ruin my fun.

27:08.120 --> 27:09.200
Get out of my way.

27:16.720 --> 27:19.160
Ning. Ning.

27:34.680 --> 27:35.800
She's not here.

27:58.680 --> 28:00.880
I'll light the lamps inside for you.

28:00.960 --> 28:02.520
That won't be necessary.

28:03.280 --> 28:05.680
Arrange the wine and dishes as before.

28:05.760 --> 28:06.880
As you wish.

28:23.320 --> 28:24.240
Remember,

28:25.360 --> 28:27.200
no matter when or where,

28:27.800 --> 28:29.400
never presume to decide for me.

28:30.800 --> 28:32.240
Even if the wrong person dies.

28:34.320 --> 28:35.320
Do you understand?

28:36.600 --> 28:37.600
Yes.

28:40.440 --> 28:41.920
I'm so sleepy.

28:42.520 --> 28:43.560
Shh, be quiet.

28:44.840 --> 28:46.680
How is the investigation going?

28:48.200 --> 28:49.800
From what I've learned,

28:50.440 --> 28:52.600
judging by the year she arrived in Lin'an,

28:53.120 --> 28:55.280
she was likely with child
while in your residence.

28:56.880 --> 28:59.120
We still need the nursemaid
brought to Lin'an

28:59.640 --> 29:01.720
to confirm her identity.

29:13.920 --> 29:14.920
Then go at once.

29:15.960 --> 29:17.080
I'll see to it immediately.

29:18.320 --> 29:19.240
Who's there?

29:23.680 --> 29:26.800
FAN'S BRAISED MEAT

29:32.120 --> 29:33.720
Sold out already?

29:34.480 --> 29:36.320
Sold out for today. Come back tomorrow.

29:37.000 --> 29:37.960
All right.

29:42.360 --> 29:43.560
This way.

29:46.680 --> 29:47.560
Make way.

29:48.440 --> 29:49.320
Make way.

29:51.000 --> 29:53.600
Mr. Li, where did
these soldiers come from?

29:55.000 --> 29:56.920
Clerk Guo mentioned yesterday

29:57.000 --> 29:59.800
that the front lines are desperate
and more grain must be taken.

29:59.880 --> 30:00.960
These are likely

30:01.680 --> 30:03.160
the soldiers sent to collect it.

30:03.760 --> 30:05.520
Wei Xuan's defeat was inevitable.

30:06.040 --> 30:07.880
I just didn't expect it
before the New Year.

30:13.000 --> 30:13.920
In Chongzhou,

30:14.600 --> 30:16.040
farmers were driven to their deaths

30:16.120 --> 30:17.440
over the levies.

30:18.000 --> 30:19.600
They say Governor He of Jizhou

30:19.680 --> 30:21.200
is a just and upright official.

30:21.280 --> 30:22.840
Let's hope he does not act the same.

30:22.920 --> 30:26.080
Grain requisition should not cost
the common people their lives.

30:28.080 --> 30:29.840
It all depends on the authorities now.

30:38.360 --> 30:39.240
What is this?

30:40.040 --> 30:41.080
It's your wages.

30:42.400 --> 30:43.720
No need. You keep it.

30:44.240 --> 30:46.000
No.

30:46.520 --> 30:47.520
We'll split it in half.

30:47.600 --> 30:49.080
You wrote hundreds of wrappers.

30:50.680 --> 30:52.320
I might lose it if I carry it with me.

30:53.480 --> 30:54.600
You keep it for me.

30:58.480 --> 31:00.720
All right, I'll keep it for you.

31:01.760 --> 31:02.640
Very well.

31:06.200 --> 31:07.440
Have you seen Ning?

31:09.440 --> 31:10.280
She's gone.

31:11.480 --> 31:12.920
Those wretches are here again.

31:17.080 --> 31:18.200
-Bao'er!
-Ning!

31:18.280 --> 31:19.440
-Bao'er!
-Who's Bao'er?

31:19.520 --> 31:20.640
My son.

31:22.000 --> 31:22.880
Fuling!

31:23.400 --> 31:24.240
Fuling!

31:24.840 --> 31:26.600
Ms. Yu, Bao'er isn't in the hidden room.

31:26.680 --> 31:27.960
Ning was just here.

31:28.040 --> 31:29.920
I stepped out for a moment,
and she vanished.

31:31.760 --> 31:33.040
Qi Min.

31:33.120 --> 31:34.360
It must have been him.

31:34.440 --> 31:35.480
Who is that?

31:35.560 --> 31:37.040
He comes here every day.

31:37.560 --> 31:39.480
Every time I see him, my skin crawls.

31:39.560 --> 31:40.720
He must have taken Bao'er.

31:40.800 --> 31:41.560
Let's split up.

31:42.400 --> 31:43.520
All right.

31:47.240 --> 31:49.760
-Has Mr. Qi left?
-I… I don't know.

31:51.880 --> 31:54.120
Ms. Yu, please calm yourself.

31:55.400 --> 31:56.600
Where is Mr. Qi?

31:56.680 --> 31:57.840
He left not long ago.

31:58.960 --> 32:00.840
Did he leave with anyone?

32:00.920 --> 32:02.480
He left in a hurry.

32:02.560 --> 32:04.440
I didn't notice whether he brought anyone.

32:05.080 --> 32:06.800
-Ms. Yu.
-Calm down.

32:17.720 --> 32:19.480
Ms. Yu, are you hurt?

32:20.000 --> 32:21.600
Let me see your hand.

32:51.200 --> 32:52.320
I'll see to it immediately.

32:53.400 --> 32:54.240
Who's there?

32:55.280 --> 32:57.040
Sir, it's me.

33:03.440 --> 33:04.920
Forgive me, sir.

33:05.000 --> 33:07.040
I accidentally knocked over the lampstand.

33:07.120 --> 33:07.960
I hope I didn't disturb you.

33:08.560 --> 33:09.560
Hand it over.

33:09.640 --> 33:11.160
-Go on.
-Enjoy yourselves.

33:17.000 --> 33:19.400
TIANYU ROOM

33:21.720 --> 33:23.080
Is this how I've taught you?

33:23.920 --> 33:26.360
No, Mother. I haven't forgotten.

33:27.240 --> 33:28.800
-I only…
-What?

33:29.480 --> 33:30.680
I only wanted to play.

33:32.720 --> 33:35.200
Do my words mean nothing to you?

33:35.280 --> 33:37.480
Why won't you listen?
Why must you run about?

33:41.520 --> 33:43.600
Qian, your hand is injured.

33:43.680 --> 33:44.800
Let me apply some medicine.

33:49.360 --> 33:51.600
Pretty Lady, please don't be angry.

33:52.200 --> 33:54.200
I fell asleep.

33:54.280 --> 33:56.400
Bao'er was only keeping me company.

33:58.920 --> 34:00.200
I won't blame you.

34:00.800 --> 34:03.560
Then may I still come play with Bao'er?

34:14.320 --> 34:15.719
Get up. The floor is cold.

34:20.239 --> 34:21.400
Mother.

34:26.159 --> 34:29.120
Qian is always so gentle with others.

34:29.199 --> 34:31.360
Why is she so harsh with her own son?

34:31.440 --> 34:34.639
Her reaction today
was harsher than even yours.

34:36.520 --> 34:37.960
I'll go see her again later.

34:38.760 --> 34:41.360
Even the closest friends
have secrets they keep to themselves.

34:41.440 --> 34:43.320
When she's ready, she'll tell you.

34:44.000 --> 34:46.400
I just don't know
what Qian has been through.

34:50.280 --> 34:52.760
Changyu, I'm sleepy.

34:54.400 --> 34:55.239
Ning's sleepy.

34:58.560 --> 34:59.640
Come here, Ning.

35:03.480 --> 35:04.520
Hold on to me.

35:11.000 --> 35:15.360
HE

35:15.440 --> 35:17.360
Dayin commands one capital
and 17 prefectures.

35:17.880 --> 35:18.960
Four lie in the northwest.

35:19.040 --> 35:20.040
PEACE AND PROSPERITY ALONG THE BORDERS

35:20.120 --> 35:22.360
Jinzhou is barren, and Chongzhou
has fallen into rebellion.

35:22.880 --> 35:25.040
Only Jizhou and Yanzhou are left.

35:26.280 --> 35:27.120
Yanzhou

35:28.040 --> 35:29.320
is a military garrison.

35:30.160 --> 35:32.080
Private grain storage and farming
are forbidden there.

35:32.160 --> 35:34.040
That means that in the northwest,

35:34.120 --> 35:36.560
only Jizhou Prefecture can supply grain.

35:37.640 --> 35:38.560
Wei Xuan

35:39.400 --> 35:41.240
clearly thinks the war in Chongzhou

35:41.320 --> 35:42.480
isn't dire enough.

35:43.080 --> 35:46.520
Wei Xuan sent troops
to seize grain by force.

35:46.600 --> 35:49.480
Even the farmers' seed grain was taken.

35:49.560 --> 35:51.520
Let alone planting next spring,

35:52.360 --> 35:55.400
they'll be fortunate
just to survive the winter.

35:56.000 --> 35:58.480
Such actions will forfeit
the people's loyalty.

36:02.400 --> 36:04.600
Why can't we collect grain?

36:05.440 --> 36:06.560
I've ordered an investigation.

36:07.400 --> 36:09.480
A month ago, a group of outside merchants

36:09.560 --> 36:11.240
bought up grain at high prices.

36:11.320 --> 36:13.760
The people kept only
seed grain and coarse grain

36:13.840 --> 36:14.680
and sold the rest.

36:15.560 --> 36:17.520
Buying up grain on the eve of war…

36:17.600 --> 36:19.880
Investigate these merchants at once.

36:20.920 --> 36:21.760
-Understood.
-Understood.

36:24.960 --> 36:26.720
Marquis, it is confirmed.

36:26.800 --> 36:28.160
The man buying grain in the city

36:28.240 --> 36:29.680
is Zhao Xun,

36:29.760 --> 36:30.600
owner of Lin'an Grain.

36:32.720 --> 36:34.240
He colluded with merchants

36:34.320 --> 36:37.240
to buy nearly 200,000 dan of grain
in Yanzhou and Jizhou at high prices.

36:38.640 --> 36:39.720
Zhao Xun?

36:43.720 --> 36:45.360
Has he been close
with anyone of note recently?

36:45.960 --> 36:48.400
Yes. A rice merchant from the capital,

36:48.480 --> 36:49.360
surnamed Qi.

36:50.760 --> 36:51.880
Qi…

36:54.640 --> 36:55.720
Mr. Qi,

36:55.800 --> 36:57.960
Ms. Yu has taken ill with a cold.

36:58.040 --> 36:59.760
She has been resting.

36:59.840 --> 37:02.160
It is truly inconvenient
for her to receive visitors.

37:02.240 --> 37:03.840
We beg your pardon, Mr. Qi.

37:06.400 --> 37:07.960
Since it is merely a cold,

37:08.040 --> 37:11.200
why not accept the medicinal broth
I had a renowned physician prepare?

37:11.280 --> 37:12.640
Not even the fox fur coat?

37:13.240 --> 37:14.640
Not enough to keep out the cold?

37:16.120 --> 37:17.160
Or

37:17.680 --> 37:19.240
is your mistress avoiding me?

37:20.800 --> 37:22.000
Not at all.

37:22.080 --> 37:24.120
She means no discourtesy.

37:24.200 --> 37:26.120
Her illness is quite serious.

37:27.080 --> 37:28.320
How serious is it?

37:29.120 --> 37:30.440
She's not dead, is she?

37:33.120 --> 37:34.400
Tell her,

37:34.480 --> 37:37.680
if I wish to see someone, I will see them.

37:42.320 --> 37:44.240
Ah, Mr. Qi has arrived.

37:44.320 --> 37:46.160
Quickly, bring wine and the finest dishes.

37:47.040 --> 37:47.920
Yes.

37:51.080 --> 37:52.600
Bring the most expensive ones.

37:56.040 --> 37:57.200
You seem quite well.

38:05.600 --> 38:06.760
Just a cold.

38:06.840 --> 38:08.040
It's no grave illness.

38:08.760 --> 38:11.560
The physician said
peace of mind matters most.

38:11.640 --> 38:13.840
No anger, no sorrow.

38:13.920 --> 38:15.240
Avoid unpleasant sights.

38:15.320 --> 38:16.920
That will aid my recovery.

38:24.280 --> 38:25.320
Stay still.

38:27.040 --> 38:29.560
We should keep our distance.
Mr. Qi, have some decorum.

38:30.160 --> 38:31.000
I said, don't move.

38:45.760 --> 38:47.000
Just now your pulse was slow,

38:47.080 --> 38:48.400
as with a chill.

38:49.480 --> 38:51.320
Now it's much faster.

39:00.120 --> 39:02.160
These remedies are exactly what you need.

39:05.520 --> 39:06.920
My thanks, Mr. Qi.

39:07.000 --> 39:10.120
It seems I'm not to your liking.

39:15.080 --> 39:16.480
How could you say that?

39:16.560 --> 39:18.400
There's no such thing.

39:18.920 --> 39:20.680
It's only that I've yet to recover.

39:20.760 --> 39:22.200
I fear I might spoil your appetite

39:22.280 --> 39:23.800
for fine dishes.

39:24.800 --> 39:26.120
I shall take my leave.

39:31.440 --> 39:32.480
Where are you going?

39:33.640 --> 39:34.680
None of your business.

39:34.760 --> 39:36.200
I asked you to take the medicine

39:36.280 --> 39:37.360
for your own sake.

39:38.520 --> 39:41.080
There are plenty of men who care for me.
Go stand in line.

39:42.560 --> 39:43.720
Who?

39:45.160 --> 39:47.240
Let go of me. Let go.

39:48.160 --> 39:49.040
What are you doing?

39:50.120 --> 39:52.640
Mr. Qi's concern for you

39:52.720 --> 39:54.440
is truly extravagant.

39:54.520 --> 39:56.640
He has booked out
the entire Yixiang Restaurant.

39:56.720 --> 39:57.760
Ms. Yu,

39:57.840 --> 39:59.440
this time you may rest properly.

40:02.080 --> 40:03.880
You've booked out my restaurant?

40:03.960 --> 40:05.240
Mr. Zhao told me

40:05.320 --> 40:06.960
they're paying 100 taels a day

40:07.040 --> 40:08.640
to book Yixiang Restaurant for ten days.

40:08.720 --> 40:09.560
For ten days,

40:10.080 --> 40:11.520
everything in Yixiang Restaurant

40:12.160 --> 40:13.000
is mine.

40:17.120 --> 40:19.080
Only 100 taels a day?

40:20.200 --> 40:21.760
Did you not bring enough silver?

40:21.840 --> 40:24.360
At least 1,000 taels a day.
Not a coin less.

40:25.200 --> 40:26.040
Can you afford that?

40:28.840 --> 40:29.920
Is that all?

40:35.200 --> 40:37.280
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

40:37.360 --> 40:38.360
How strange.

40:38.440 --> 40:39.560
That's strange.

40:40.480 --> 40:42.560
Ms. Yu gave no notice.

40:45.280 --> 40:47.600
-Excuse me.
-"We are closed for renovations.

40:47.680 --> 40:49.880
We ask for our patrons' understanding."

40:53.160 --> 40:54.960
Why close so suddenly?

40:55.040 --> 40:56.120
Where is Ms. Yu?

40:56.880 --> 40:59.880
We came to work this morning
and only then learned of it.

40:59.960 --> 41:01.040
We haven't seen her.

41:02.160 --> 41:03.120
That's strange.

41:05.480 --> 41:07.000
Mrs. Man. Mr. Li.

41:07.080 --> 41:08.280
Why is Yixiang closed?

41:08.360 --> 41:10.280
It was booked out by Mr. Qi.

41:10.360 --> 41:12.240
He dismissed us for a few days,

41:12.320 --> 41:13.560
saying he had no need of us.

41:13.640 --> 41:15.600
Even the front door is locked.

41:15.680 --> 41:17.160
In all my years working here,

41:17.240 --> 41:18.600
I've never seen anything like this.

41:18.680 --> 41:20.800
-Indeed.
-What about Qian?

41:20.880 --> 41:22.920
She was ill yesterday.
She must still be inside.

41:23.000 --> 41:24.120
Yes.

41:24.960 --> 41:25.800
I'll go take a look.

41:26.440 --> 41:27.440
The doors are locked.

41:27.520 --> 41:29.200
You're not thinking of scaling…

41:34.480 --> 41:35.440
She really did.

41:39.760 --> 41:40.880
Qian.

41:42.520 --> 41:43.720
Qian.

41:44.880 --> 41:46.880
-Qian.
-Don't come closer! Help!

41:48.040 --> 41:49.800
Don't come closer. Stay back.

41:52.240 --> 41:53.280
-Qian.
-No…

41:53.800 --> 41:54.760
No.

41:55.600 --> 41:57.040
-No…
-Qian.

41:57.120 --> 41:58.160
Stay back.

41:58.240 --> 41:59.640
-Qian.
-Stay back!

42:00.920 --> 42:02.640
No… No!

42:04.800 --> 42:06.320
-Changyu.
-It's all right now.

42:10.320 --> 42:11.280
What's wrong?

42:11.360 --> 42:12.880
What nightmare frightened you so?

42:15.280 --> 42:16.440
I dreamed of a madman.

42:20.400 --> 42:21.800
Stay back!

42:21.880 --> 42:23.320
A masked madman.

42:31.360 --> 42:32.200
Here.

42:35.600 --> 42:39.080
Mrs. Man said Yixiang
was booked by a gentleman named Qi.

42:39.160 --> 42:40.040
What's going on?

42:44.600 --> 42:45.600
No.

42:46.160 --> 42:47.920
I dare not accept this arrangement.

42:49.440 --> 42:50.680
What happened?

42:51.280 --> 42:53.080
I deliberately named 1,000 taels,

42:53.160 --> 42:54.080
and he still agreed.

42:55.840 --> 42:57.520
The more I think, the worse it feels.

42:57.600 --> 42:59.040
So I closed up to avoid him.

43:02.760 --> 43:06.720
Could it be that he simply fancies you?

43:12.120 --> 43:13.040
I don't know.

43:14.560 --> 43:16.280
I just feel

43:16.880 --> 43:17.920
it can't be so simple.

43:20.200 --> 43:21.840
How about I toss him in a sack,

43:21.920 --> 43:23.400
beat him soundly, and make him talk?

43:24.920 --> 43:27.080
Beating him won't solve anything
in the long run.

43:27.160 --> 43:29.040
Guo Dali is proof enough.

43:30.520 --> 43:33.000
Besides, booking
the entire place isn't unlawful.

43:35.680 --> 43:36.560
You are right.

43:37.840 --> 43:39.960
This relentless pestering is unbearable.

43:41.320 --> 43:43.760
I've seen this sort
of money-flinging arrogance before.

43:46.040 --> 43:48.000
If he truly only fancies me,

43:48.520 --> 43:50.360
to make him give up entirely,

43:50.440 --> 43:52.440
we must cut off his hopes at the root.

43:55.640 --> 43:57.200
We must let him think

43:57.760 --> 43:59.240
I am already wed.

43:59.320 --> 44:00.720
Then he'll know to retreat.

44:00.800 --> 44:01.920
But you're not married.

44:02.640 --> 44:03.520
You are.

44:03.600 --> 44:05.440
I am. You're not.

44:35.640 --> 44:38.480
‎THE BOOK OF SONGS: AIRS OF ZHENG

47:05.200 --> 47:08.480
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

47:08.560 --> 47:09.480
